    <!-- Help -->
    <string name="help_title">Help</string>
    <string name="help_text">
        <b>Getting Started with eXcap</b><br /><br />

        1. <b>Start Capture</b><br />
        Tap the capture button in the Capture tab or use the floating action button. Grant VPN permission when prompted.<br /><br />

        2. <b>Monitor Traffic</b><br />
        View real-time connections, packets, and statistics in their respective tabs.<br /><br />

        3. <b>Inspect Connections</b><br />
        Tap any connection to see detailed information including headers and payload.<br /><br />

        4. <b>Filter Traffic</b><br />
        Use protocol filter chips or the search bar to find specific traffic.<br /><br />

        5. <b>TLS Decryption</b><br />
        Install the CA certificate from Settings to decrypt HTTPS traffic.<br /><br />

        6. <b>Export Data</b><br />
        Save captured traffic as PCAP files from the Settings menu.<br /><br />

        <b>Note:</b> eXcap requires Android 8.0 (API 26) or higher.
    </string>

